Citizens’ rights, on the other hand, asked the press several times before the law came into force: What does the whole mean?
What changes does the regulation bring to show language skills, both for the Russians and for the guest workers?
First and foremost, opposition to the Migration Authority’s spokespersons, it is about reducing the number of forced workers.
